  "title" : "Invalid escape sequence (valid ones are \\b \\t \\n \\f \\r \\&quot; \\&#39; \\\\ )",
  "body" : "<p>I am trying to read a file into my Java program using java.util.Scanner and I get the above message when I enter the code below (I am new to java) - can anyone help? (I looked at a similar message someone got with their own code, but it was too complex for me to use in my example!). I have Windows 7.</p>\n\n<pre><code>BufferedReader job = new BufferedReader\n               (new FileReader(\"\\My Documents\\JOBS\\newfile.txt\"));\n</code></pre>\n"
